snippet.title: Dr Tony Hampton
snippet.description: Dr. Tony Hampton is a Family Physician who since 1998 has treated patient with multiple chronic conditions. He is a board certified Family Physician, a Certified Physician Executive (CPE) and has earned a MBA from the University of Phoenix. The medical  condition which has had the greatest impact in his life both in his family and as a physician has been diabetes inspiring him to give his patients a useful tool by authoring a book entitled: Fix Your Diet, Fix Your Diabetes with a release date, fall 2016.  He has been a regular speaker for the American Diabetes Association at its annual Expo.  His passion to empower patients with knowledge was the driving force behind his desire to become an author and write about ways diet can help improve not only diabetes but other health conditions.  His website provides links to his social media accounts and blogs at drtonyhampton.com
